title: COVID-19 Special: Jewel Burks Solomon - Opportunity for Creative Thinkers
description: Carla Harris checks in with Jewel Burks Solomon, head of Google for Startups in the U.S. and co-founder of Partpic, which she sold to Amazon in 2016. Jewel discusses the importance of self-care and how she's advising companies to think creatively in this time of COVID-19.
